column2: Longevity Acquisition Corporation is a China-based blank check company. The Company is formed for the purpose of acquiring, engaging in a share exchange, share reconstruction and amalgamation. The Company purchases all or substantially all of the assets of, entering into contractual arrangements with, or engaging in any other similar business combination with one or more businesses or entities.
Yongda International Tower No. 2277, Longevity Road Pudong District
